LICENSE TERMS
================================================================================
This source code is made publicly available for the following permitted
purposes only:

  1. Transparency and public verification of the protocol's design,
     security properties, and compliance posture.

  2. Academic study, educational reference, and scholarly citation.

  3. Independent security audit, peer review, and reproducible
     pre-audit verification per the procedures documented in
     docs/security/ of this repository.

  4. Personal, non-commercial experimentation in a strictly local
     test environment, with no public deployment.

The following uses are EXPRESSLY NOT PERMITTED without prior written
authorization from the InfraVeritas Energy Team:

  - Commercial use of any kind, including but not limited to
    operating a derivative protocol, providing services based on
    this code, or incorporating this code into commercial products.

  - Redistribution in source or binary form, in whole or in part,
    whether modified or unmodified.

  - Creation of derivative works intended for public deployment,
    commercial use, or external distribution. Public forks on
    GitHub or equivalent platforms intended for production
    deployment are not permitted.

  - Production deployment on any public blockchain, testnet
    intended to serve real users, or off-chain infrastructure
    serving production traffic.

  - Practice of any method, system, or technique covered by
    pending or issued patent claims referenced above.


