remain subject to their respective upstream licenses, which are
preserved within those directories. Nothing in this license is
intended to override or supersede those upstream license terms.

The IPAS Verification Standard v1.0 specification document (separate
PDF artifact available at https://infraveritas.pro/) is published
under terms documented within that specification and may have
different license conditions for the standard itself versus reference
implementations of the standard.


